metadata.description: Community Collaboration Experiment  1st)�Mint the Free Basic Ghost NFT? - 2nd) Each NFT has a random property file attached (head, body, etc)? - 3rd) Download the file, and Turn that attribute into your own! ?4th) After creating, submit your art to our Collab Engine to turn make your art officially awkward - ?5th) Your Minted Ghost will be updated featuring your addition, and you set your new price!? - 6th) After each sale, a new file is added to the listing so the next person can create the next attribute - ?7th) Keep passing it along till the Ghost is complete! Lets see what we can create together! Remember.. Get Ghosted and Be Awkward!
